products.title: Modular Kitchen Alfa
products.description: "The goal of Mangiamo Modular Kitchens is to elevate cooking to an art form,  by fusing functionality and aesthetics, while still emphasizing on ergonomics  and utility."

features.title: Materials
features.desc: Mangiamo is equipped with high quality raw materials and  German hardware and built to meet global quality standards.

features.title: Look
features.desc: Neutrals done right! This modern orange and grey kitchen is  packed with all you need to cook up a storm.

features.title: Quality
features.desc: It's compact in structure, yet provides ample storage space.  The overhead wall cabinets and neatly arranged base units are  adequate for all your needs.
